%% Sequence - Notification sending

sequenceDiagram
  participant System
  participant Notifier as NotificationService
  participant Email as EmailProvider
  participant User

  System->>Notifier: Create notification record
  Notifier->>Email: Send email (template)
  Email-->>Notifier: Delivery status
  Notifier-->>System: Update notification status
  Notifier-->>User: Email delivered
